            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            管制镓和锗之后，美国准备“捡破烂”          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                                                                    <span role="link" tabindex="0" id="js_author_name" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta_link weui-wa-hotarea" datarewardsn="" datatimestamp="" datacanreward="0">申鹏</span>                                                                            </span>                                                                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                平原公子              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">平原公子</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">pingyuangongzi</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">讲人间故事，说是非曲直！</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>            <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" style="display: none;">发表于<span id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                      </div>                                                                                                                  <div id="js_tags" class="article-tag__list" data-len="2">                                        <div class="article-tag-card__title">收录于合集</div>              <div class="article-tags">                                                      <div class="article-tag__item-wrp js_tag weui-wa-hotarea js_wx_tap_highlight wx_tap_link" data-url="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/appmsgalbum?__biz=MzA3NzY3NjUzNQ==&amp;action=getalbum&amp;album_id=1690122287443738636#wechat_redirect" data-tag_id="" data-album_id="1690122287443738636" data-tag_source="3" role="link" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="js_article_tag_name__1690122287443738636 js_a11y_comma js_article_tag_num__1690122287443738636 js_article_tag_tips__1690122287443738636">                      <span aria-hidden="true" id="js_article_tag_name__1690122287443738636" class="article-tag__item">#美国</span>                                              <span aria-hidden="true" class="article-tag__item-num">                          <span id="js_article_tag_num__1690122287443738636">304</span>                          <span id="js_article_tag_tips__1690122287443738636" class="weui-hidden_abs">个</span>                        </span>                                          </div>                                      <div class="article-tag__item-wrp js_tag weui-wa-hotarea js_wx_tap_highlight wx_tap_link" data-url="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/appmsgalbum?__biz=MzA3NzY3NjUzNQ==&amp;action=getalbum&amp;album_id=3036004351036801030#wechat_redirect" data-tag_id="" data-album_id="3036004351036801030" data-tag_source="1" role="link" tabindex="0" aria-labelledby="js_article_tag_name__3036004351036801030 js_a11y_comma js_article_tag_num__3036004351036801030 js_article_tag_tips__3036004351036801030">                      <span aria-hidden="true" id="js_article_tag_name__3036004351036801030" class="article-tag__item">#镓和锗</span>                                              <span aria-hidden="true" class="article-tag__item-num">                          <span id="js_article_tag_num__3036004351036801030">1</span>                          <span id="js_article_tag_tips__3036004351036801030" class="weui-hidden_abs">个</span>                        </span>                                          </div>                                                </div>                      </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p data-first-child="" data-pid="lZM4z7yu" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io">美国国防部计划在年底前首次签订“从废品中回收镓”的合同。</p><p data-first-child="" data-pid="lZM4z7yu">“因为镓对生产尖端军用雷达和其他半导体系统至关重要”。</p><p data-first-child="" data-pid="lZM4z7yu">一贯奢侈浪费的美帝居然要捡破烂了。</p><p data-pid="XhDu4i3y">你以前劝他们过点节省、环保、低碳的生活，他们是死都不乐意的，自从咱们管制了镓和锗的出口，老美居然试图勤俭持家过日子了。</p><p data-pid="3VoXntf2">你看，我们强大起来、发展起来是一件好事，当我们掌握了长产业链的氮化镓冶炼产业，当我们的农民都开始用上单人便携氮化镓相控阵雷达，当我们开始卡它们脖子的时候……桀骜不驯的帝国主义居然变得如此乖巧！温驯！</p><p data-pid="QkhZC_Dx">他们不抱怨、不发脾气、而是自己反思，从自身出发，用捡垃圾去解决问题——这对美国来说是个巨大的进步。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-ratio="0.5481481481481482" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/1hbMm9fxQOJJOexjRPwALIicsIIEtGkI081Z5PNicQq1ofot3kK1uleEVjz0XzdQAHLfv5VXvSlMib8Oumw3zib5Rg/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="1080" style=""></p><p data-pid="RGxqFN4Y">捡垃圾回收氮化镓是个好主意，只不过，以3亿美国人的电子产品消耗量，以美国全球第一军费的装备采购数量……这点垃圾简直是杯水车薪，更何况，垃圾回收处理也是个长链产业，需要上下游很多工业体系的配合，从垃圾里炼宝贝，能力最强、技术最先进、配套产业最齐全的国家，也在东方。</p><p data-pid="9Y7xrh6i">对于今天的美国来说，重建一套氧化铝工业生产体系千难万难，重建一套高科技垃圾处理、“变废为宝”的产业，更是难于登天。</p><p data-pid="X5lsmlKY">有“上中下”三策，献与美帝：</p><p data-pid="DCxelo-Y">上策：独立自主、自力更生，全民大炼“镓锗”，美国人民要为国家想，一辆电车、一台电脑、一部手机、一个快充头都不能留，人人当炼金术士，家家架坩埚火炉，用群众的力量突破封锁。</p><p data-pid="EvOo2mnl">中策：进口不了镓、锗，那就从中国高价进口电动汽车、手机、电脑、快充头……回去请上次踩缝纫机做口罩的美军和囚犯慢慢拆去，用“工匠精神”拯救美国。</p><p data-pid="r2c82u7S">下策：捡垃圾是个好习惯，但美国本土这点垃圾是不够的，可以高价从东方进口海量电子垃圾，引进东方的垃圾处理产业……既环保、又能创造新的就业和经济增长点，一举三得，从此美国成为全世界的垃圾回收处理厂，善莫大焉。</p><p data-pid="piTh75kU">其实还有个“上上策”：那就是<strong>打开chatGPT，输入“给我变出100吨氮化镓”。</strong></p><figure data-size="normal" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/1hbMm9fxQOJJOexjRPwALIicsIIEtGkI0WSGrYxOI90uat5G2A1uzTJgUvCkRNulfk8HfuEDSibOvVLapibN0ZFrg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="other" data-w="1080" height="608" style="margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;display: block;cursor: zoom-in;animation: 0.5s ease-in 0s 1 normal none running animation-1yvu044;" width="1080"></figure><figure data-size="normal"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="0.4925925925925926" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/1hbMm9fxQOJJOexjRPwALIicsIIEtGkI0vEZo0Yb1fZoYibWPa909HFvxg5VD4nSRu0uWdUnJPpYcvWJCMTVTf4A/640?wx_fmt=png" data-type="png" data-w="1080"></figure><p><br></p><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-profile class="js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-id="MzA3NzY3NjUzNQ==" data-headimg="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/1hbMm9fxQOLRB0Fic2ALKqKicj6icF5JxBC3RIqt57DRe7TxSXvRiao4oBWUiaChKGl4cDZAnSXtZh6bsPicotQ3BDwA/0?wx_fmt=png" data-nickname="平原公子" data-alias="pingyuangongzi" data-signature="讲人间故事，说是非曲直！" data-from="0" data-is_biz_ban="0"></mp-common-profile></section><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-profile class="js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-id="MzI0OTc1MjI1MA==" data-headimg="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/AaqjwmBS9LcwmYQSZESwKbfcHxb2KHfqia37KxyB4oDmSv4fzEbJuAyFeEuxHfYjaEFm81uviadvd3hJU1jzaxcw/0?wx_fmt=png" data-nickname="唐赛儿" data-alias="weiruji210" data-signature="作家，文史工作者" data-from="0" data-is_biz_ban="0"></mp-common-profile></section><figure data-size="normal"><br></figure><p><br></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="1463411955" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>              </div>    </div>]]></description>
